title: "home-security-auditor"
abstract: "Read-only home network security auditor for Windows + WSL2. Combines nmap, PowerShell host checks, router admin scraping, and credential exposure detection. Produces structured JSON findings and an optional GPT-5.5-generated kill-chain report with prioritized remediation. Personal use only — scan only networks you own."
